umb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Feather_Hat\" title=\"Feather Hat\"><img alt=\"Feather Hat\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Feather_Hat.png?775eb5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Feather_Hat\" title=\"Feather Hat\">Feather Hat</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bush_Hat\" title=\"Bush Hat\"><img alt=\"Bush Hat\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Bush_Hat.png?46fdef\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bush_Hat\" title=\"Bush Hat\">Bush Hat</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter_Hat\" title=\"Winter Hat\"><img alt=\"Winter Hat\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Winter_Hat.png?deb1d6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter_Hat\" title=\"Winter Hat\">Winter Hat</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dapper_Vest\" title=\"Dapper Vest\"><img alt=\"Dapper Vest\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dapper_Vest.png?cd44ca\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dapper_Vest\" title=\"Dapper Vest\">Dapper Vest</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Breezy_Vest\" title=\"Breezy Vest\"><img alt=\"Breezy Vest\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Breezy_Vest.png?d84aa0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/B